z0 = other mortality

```{r}
library(readr)
parameters <-read.csv("~/Marine Biology MSC/Thesis Project/Data/MIZER code/mizer/inst/algarve/parameters.csv")
winf <-c(parameters$w_inf)
species <-C(parameters$Species)
z0pre <-(0.6)

names(z0)<-species
```
